Adjust download limits to accurately reflect subscription tiers and entitlements

Implement granular download validation logic in the frontend and backend to enforce subscription-based download limits (e.g., 2 per month for free users, 1 per month for premium subscribers) per subject, while ensuring special access users and yearly subscribers have unlimited downloads. Includes toast notifications for limit breaches.

